data.text: @aparanjape @SidShirole @AjitPawarSpeaks @mohol_murlidhar बागेतले कामचुकार मजूर आणि उद्यान विभागातील कामचुकार कर्मचारी. आपल्या देशात कर्तव्य म्हणजे एकच. फुकटचा पगार घेणे. आणि वर माज करणे. सरकार कुणाचेही असो. समाजातील मानसिकता कधी बदलेल कोण जाणे.

@SidShirole @AjitPawarSpeaks What is the status of Pre primary schools. Are they allowed to remain shut or are you planning to open them? Paid booster is the best way forward instead of waiting for 9 months after the 2nd shot.

@SidShirole @AjitPawarSpeaks Preschools should also return to Normalcy immediately ! These kids have not seen or played with any other group of kids ever since they are born. Will later become difficult for them to accept others! 

@narendramodi @AUThackeray @Dev_Fadnavis @SidShirole @AjitPawarSpeaks
@SidShirole Why can’t the municipality do vaccine drives just like they did polio drives?  Take the vaccine to the people.
